msg.msgText: imaserver user delete "Item1=value" ... SYNTAX: imaserver user delete help imaserver user delete "Item1=value" ... EXAMPLE: imaserver user delete "UserID=webUser1" "Type=WebUI" imaserver user delete "UserID=msgUser1" "Type=Messaging" Configuration items are: UserID The user ID. Type The user type. Only [WebUI] or [Messaging] are allowed. NOTES: 1. "UserID", "Type" are required items. 2. All "Key=value" pair must be enclosed within double quotation marks.
